--train : trains on the dataset
--dataset {value} : sets the dataset, default train_AIDA, options are given in datasets.py
--bundle {id} : sets all the hyperparameters to predefined defaults, default '0' (ment-norm optimum bundle)

To use the model in evaluation mode on a dataset you will want to:
- Run "main.py --train"
- Run "main.py --dataset {evalsetname}"

